Package umlcodeconverter.relationship

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeneralizationConverter
    Provides a static method adding a CodeElement converted out of the supplier UmlElement of an UmlRelationship of type UmlRelationshipType.GENERALIZATION to the CodeElement converted out of the client UmlElement of this UmlRelationship.
    InterfaceRealizationConverter
    Provides a static method adding a CodeElement converted out of the supplier UmlElement of an UmlRelationship of type UmlRelationshipType.GENERALIZATION to the CodeElement converted out of the client UmlElement of this UmlRelationship.
    RelationshipConverter
    Provides a static method delegating the conversion of UmlRelationships of type UmlRelationshipType.GENERALIZATION to the GeneralizationConverter and those of type UmlRelationshipType.INTERFACEREALIZATION to the InterfaceRealizationConverter
